Oh, my God.

377
00:17:27,590 --> 00:17:30,100
快速烤面包机
An Easy Bake Oven!

378
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:33,100
但我还是个小孩的时候 我就想要一个
I've wanted one of these ever since I was a little girl.

379
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:35,310
就是这个东西
In this exact model.

380
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:38,790
我从来都没有跟你说过 你怎么知道的?
I never told you that. How did you know?

381
00:17:39,370 --> 00:17:41,660
这是我们和好之后的第一个圣诞
It's our first Christmas since we got back together.

382
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:43,340
我向送她点与众不同的
I want to get her something really special.

383
00:17:43,370 --> 00:17:45,130
所以我想送他个自动点唱机
So I'm getting her a jukebox.

384
