I mean how do you choose your favorite passage?

417
00:19:29,940 --> 00:19:34,090
这个是圣经里面 有太多太多的经典了...
It's the Bible; there's so many... great ones...

418
00:19:34,100 --> 00:19:36,510
黑色通缉令那节很不错
That one from Pulp Fiction's pretty cool.

419
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:39,100
我去开门 查瑞迪 你来吧
Ooh, I'll get it. Charity, I'm tapping you in.

420
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:41,750
